WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.000
{\an8}<b><font color="#9CD5FF">One Pace Premium</font></b>
Keep the project alive: <font color="#a8c7fa">ko-fi.com/not6ip</font>

2
00:01:50.050 --> 00:01:57.680
The Silent Man

3
00:02:03.650 --> 00:02:05.020
You!

4
00:02:05.020 --> 00:02:08.400
You made a fool of me...

5
00:02:08.980 --> 00:02:13.070
How dare you mock
my pirate blood?!

6
00:02:13.070 --> 00:02:15.450
Stop it, Usopp!

7
00:02:36.180 --> 00:02:37.720
Klahadore...

8
00:02:38.600 --> 00:02:40.100
Are you there, Klahadore?

9
00:02:41.600 --> 00:02:43.230
Klahadore...

10
00:02:46.230 --> 00:02:48.190
M-Merry!

11
00:02:48.820 --> 00:02:49.900
Merry!

12
00:02:50.690 --> 00:02:53.030
What's wrong?! What happened?!

13
00:02:53.030 --> 00:02:54.400
Open your eyes, Merry!

14
00:02:55.910 --> 00:02:57.780
Please don't die!

15
00:02:56.780 --> 00:02:59.030
M-Miss Kaya...

16
00:02:59.030 --> 00:03:01.870
Th-Thank goodness you're all right...

17
00:03:02.330 --> 00:03:03.250
Merry...!

18
00:03:07.290 --> 00:03:10.500
Merry? Wh-Who did this?!

19
00:03:10.500 --> 00:03:11.880
Klahadore!

20
00:03:11.880 --> 00:03:14.800
He... attacked me!

21
00:03:16.720 --> 00:03:21.220
He... He was a pirate all along!

22
00:03:21.970 --> 00:03:24.810
Wh-What are you talking about...?

23
00:03:24.810 --> 00:03:30.940
He only got close to you
so he could steal your estate...

24
00:03:44.830 --> 00:03:45.750
Then...

25
00:03:46.410 --> 00:03:49.330
what Usopp said yesterday was true...

26
00:03:50.880 --> 00:03:53.840
Yes, come to think of it...

27
00:03:54.340 --> 00:03:59.390
When he learned the truth,
he did his best to help us!

28
00:03:59.390 --> 00:04:05.310
Yet, not a single one of us
even tried to hear him out!

29
00:04:06.640 --> 00:04:08.440
You gotta run, Kaya!

30
00:04:08.440 --> 00:04:09.730
They're gonna kill you!

31
00:04:11.730 --> 00:04:13.610
But you gotta escape for now!

32
00:04:16.030 --> 00:04:21.660
We gave shelter to the true villain
while we spurned that brave lad!

33
00:04:21.660 --> 00:04:26.500
He ran himself ragged
for the sake of the village...

34
00:04:27.460 --> 00:04:29.620
and we drove him away...!

35
00:04:32.210 --> 00:04:35.510
S-Someone help! Merry is...!

36
00:04:34.130 --> 00:04:35.510
Miss Kaya!

37
00:04:35.510 --> 00:04:36.710
It's no use...

38
00:04:38.670 --> 00:04:43.180
The rest of the staff has been
on leave since yesterday.

39
00:04:43.810 --> 00:04:45.470
No...

40
00:04:45.470 --> 00:04:46.720
Then I'll...

41
00:04:46.720 --> 00:04:48.810
You must remain calm!

42
00:04:49.520 --> 00:04:52.150
They haven't enacted their plan yet!

43
00:04:52.150 --> 00:04:56.480
You must think
things through carefully!

44
00:04:58.780 --> 00:05:03.120
If Klahadore wants your
mansion and your fortune...

45
00:05:03.120 --> 00:05:05.990
then just hand it over to him!

46
00:05:05.990 --> 00:05:09.370
None of it is worth risking your life!

47
00:05:11.960 --> 00:05:12.960
You're right.

48
00:05:13.330 --> 00:05:14.750
Cruel as it may be,

49
00:05:14.750 --> 00:05:18.710
you're the only one who
can stop Klahadore now.

50
00:05:20.220 --> 00:05:21.800
Can you do it?

51
00:05:21.800 --> 00:05:25.350
This isn't your responsibility, but...

52
00:05:26.180 --> 00:05:31.140
Even I know this isn't just
something I can run away from...

53
00:05:32.020 --> 00:05:33.770
I understand that fully!

54
00:05:35.110 --> 00:05:38.530
I'll talk things over with Klahadore!

55
00:05:41.780 --> 00:05:45.200
What?! That butler went to the shore?!

56
00:05:45.200 --> 00:05:48.290
Yeah! And he had a scary
look on his face!

57
00:05:50.080 --> 00:05:51.620
Hey, wake up!

58
00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:55.710
But I should still be in bed...

59
00:05:55.710 --> 00:05:58.090
This is no time to be sleeping!

60
00:05:58.090 --> 00:06:00.050
We could be in trouble!

61
00:06:00.050 --> 00:06:01.420
Huh?

62
00:06:03.050 --> 00:06:05.680
I think pirates really
are going to attack us.

63
00:06:06.430 --> 00:06:10.140
Our captain said he was lying,
but I think that was a lie!

64
00:06:10.640 --> 00:06:11.770
I think so too!

65
00:06:12.770 --> 00:06:16.730
Me too! Something was kinda off
about the captain yesterday!

66
00:06:16.730 --> 00:06:18.440
Oh, it's Miss Kaya!

67
00:06:18.440 --> 00:06:19.940
She's alright!

68
00:06:30.410 --> 00:06:33.330
She looks worried about something.

69
00:06:33.330 --> 00:06:36.330
Miss Kaya, walking outside
all by herself...

70
00:06:36.330 --> 00:06:37.880
Something's up!

71
00:06:37.880 --> 00:06:40.460
Something's gotta be up!

72
00:06:44.010 --> 00:06:46.470
Come forth, Meowban Brothers!

73
00:06:50.140 --> 00:06:53.140
Sham
Ship Guard
Black Cat Pirates

74
00:06:50.680 --> 00:06:53.140
You called, Captain Jango?

75
00:06:53.310 --> 00:06:56.440
Buchi
Ship Guard
Black Cat Pirates

76
00:06:55.020 --> 00:06:56.440
You called?

77
00:06:56.440 --> 00:06:57.940
Sham...

78
00:06:57.940 --> 00:06:58.860
...and Buchi!

79
00:06:58.860 --> 00:07:02.820
– Together, we are the Meowban Brothers!
– Together, we are the Meowban Brothers!

80
00:07:06.160 --> 00:07:07.660
Buchi! Sham!

81
00:07:07.660 --> 00:07:12.160
We need to get up
this hill no matter what...

82
00:07:12.160 --> 00:07:14.040
but someone's in the way.

83
00:07:14.500 --> 00:07:15.670
Get rid of him.

84
00:07:16.460 --> 00:07:19.590
Th-There's no way we can do that!

85
00:07:19.590 --> 00:07:21.210
Right, Buchi?!

86
00:07:21.210 --> 00:07:23.920
Yeah, he looks strong!

87
00:07:24.260 --> 00:07:25.340
Huh?

88
00:07:25.800 --> 00:07:29.100
Besides, we're just
supposed to guard the ship!

89
00:07:29.100 --> 00:07:32.930
Yeah, that's right! I'm not sure
why you'd make us fight...

90
00:07:32.930 --> 00:07:37.350
H-Huh? I thought he said
this was their trump card...

91
00:07:37.350 --> 00:07:39.810
Sham! Get going already!

92
00:07:39.810 --> 00:07:41.690
What?! M-Me?!

93
00:07:41.690 --> 00:07:42.690
Now!

94
00:07:42.690 --> 00:07:45.150
A-Alright, I'll do it!

95
00:07:45.530 --> 00:07:47.410
He's crying!

96
00:07:47.410 --> 00:07:49.160
What's his game plan?

97
00:07:50.410 --> 00:07:52.410
Why make this poor guy fight?

98
00:07:52.410 --> 00:07:53.740
Hey, you!

99
00:07:53.740 --> 00:07:54.910
Get ready!

100
00:07:54.910 --> 00:07:57.920
I'm gonna scratch you up
real good with these claws!

101
00:08:00.210 --> 00:08:02.210
What the hell are you up to?!

102
00:08:02.670 --> 00:08:05.010
Hey, you! Stop or I'll cut you in half!

103
00:08:07.090 --> 00:08:08.220
Good luck with that!

104
00:08:08.220 --> 00:08:09.220
What?!

105
00:08:13.350 --> 00:08:14.180
What the hell?!

106
00:08:14.180 --> 00:08:15.220
You!

107
00:08:16.020 --> 00:08:18.270
I got you to drop
your guard, didn't I?

108
00:08:18.270 --> 00:08:23.020
I'm impressed you could still block
after my poor-little-kitty-cat routine!

109
00:08:23.860 --> 00:08:25.530
You might have a bit of skill,

110
00:08:25.530 --> 00:08:29.570
but I wouldn't underestimate
Sham of the Meowban Brothers!

111
00:08:33.740 --> 00:08:37.960
Missing something?
Well, don't look at me!

112
00:08:38.660 --> 00:08:39.670
There it is...

113
00:08:39.670 --> 00:08:41.130
Cat Burglary...

114
00:08:41.540 --> 00:08:43.630
Give those swords back!

115
00:08:43.630 --> 00:08:48.050
Give them back?
But you already have a sword.

116
00:08:51.090 --> 00:08:53.220
These are just in the way.

117
00:09:00.020 --> 00:09:01.310
Perfect!

118
00:09:01.310 --> 00:09:03.400
That lightened the load!

119
00:09:03.400 --> 00:09:07.070
Show a little respect
for other people's stuff!

120
00:09:11.160 --> 00:09:12.910
Bastard!

121
00:09:15.030 --> 00:09:15.700
What?!

122
00:09:16.910 --> 00:09:18.700
I wonder what you actually cut!

123
00:09:18.700 --> 00:09:20.710
I'm as limber as a cat!

124
00:09:23.460 --> 00:09:25.170
You're up, Buchi!

125
00:09:25.170 --> 00:09:26.090
Get 'im!

126
00:09:26.090 --> 00:09:27.960
On it, Sham!

127
00:09:28.670 --> 00:09:30.970
Cat...

128
00:09:33.640 --> 00:09:35.470
Astrophe!

129
00:09:37.640 --> 00:09:39.270
Damn!

130
00:09:39.270 --> 00:09:40.600
He got away!

131
00:09:40.600 --> 00:09:43.350
Hey! Hold him down better, Sham!

132
00:09:43.350 --> 00:09:44.730
My bad!

133
00:09:44.730 --> 00:09:47.780
This meathead is way
stronger than I thought!

134
00:09:48.530 --> 00:09:50.280
What the hell?!

135
00:09:50.280 --> 00:09:55.200
One hit from that guy would
pulverize every bone in my body!

136
00:09:55.570 --> 00:09:57.160
He's not getting away this time!

137
00:09:57.160 --> 00:09:58.370
That's right!

138
00:09:58.870 --> 00:10:02.000
One-sword style isn't really
my specialty, but...

139
00:10:03.040 --> 00:10:05.000
Let's go, Buchi!

140
00:10:05.420 --> 00:10:07.210
Yeah! Let's do it, Sham!

141
00:10:07.210 --> 00:10:10.920
– Pussy Willow March!
– Pussy Willow March!

142
00:10:18.350 --> 00:10:20.810
This is bad! They have Zoro
on the defensive!

143
00:10:24.060 --> 00:10:25.560
What are you doing?!

144
00:10:25.560 --> 00:10:29.320
He's not gonna get anywhere
just blocking their attacks!

145
00:10:29.320 --> 00:10:30.900
I'm gonna help him out!

146
00:10:30.900 --> 00:10:32.530
Take this!

147
00:10:32.530 --> 00:10:33.740
Lead Star!

148
00:10:39.950 --> 00:10:41.120
Gotcha!

149
00:10:47.130 --> 00:10:50.130
Hey, why are you hitting him?!
He's on our side!

150
00:10:50.880 --> 00:10:52.340
No, that's not it!

151
00:10:52.340 --> 00:10:55.890
It's almost like he got
hit on purpose...

152
00:10:55.890 --> 00:10:57.760
Huh? On purpose?!

153
00:10:59.810 --> 00:11:01.810
Usopp, you dumbass!

154
00:11:01.810 --> 00:11:03.020
Do you want to die?!

155
00:11:07.520 --> 00:11:09.230
You don't suppose...

156
00:11:09.730 --> 00:11:12.230
we're the ones who just got saved?

157
00:11:12.230 --> 00:11:16.240
If you had hit them with
your slingshot...

158
00:11:16.240 --> 00:11:19.370
they probably would've
come after us instead!

159
00:11:20.030 --> 00:11:21.240
So he...

160
00:11:21.790 --> 00:11:24.000
This is no time for that!

161
00:11:27.250 --> 00:11:28.540
Damn it!

162
00:11:28.540 --> 00:11:31.880
If I just had one more sword...!

163
00:11:34.130 --> 00:11:35.930
I'm gonna get his swords!

164
00:11:35.930 --> 00:11:38.010
If I get them back to him,
he'll win for sure!

165
00:11:38.010 --> 00:11:39.470
In that case, I'll do it!

166
00:11:40.350 --> 00:11:41.850
Don't push yourself!

167
00:11:41.850 --> 00:11:43.680
You can barely even stand!

168
00:11:45.430 --> 00:11:46.390
Wait! Nami!

169
00:12:06.580 --> 00:12:07.620
Nami!

170
00:12:07.960 --> 00:12:10.250
What do you need swords for?

171
00:12:25.220 --> 00:12:29.480
Er... I-I can explain!

172
00:12:33.400 --> 00:12:37.490
Dawn has long since passed...

173
00:12:37.490 --> 00:12:41.870
so it seemed odd that the plan
wasn't making any progress.

174
00:12:42.410 --> 00:12:44.740
C-Captain Kuro!

175
00:12:44.740 --> 00:12:46.370
W-We're dead!

176
00:12:52.840 --> 00:12:54.300
Things can't get any worse!

177
00:13:08.140 --> 00:13:11.770
What in the hell is going on here?!

178
00:13:16.480 --> 00:13:20.320
To think that mere children
have kept you from progressing...

179
00:13:20.950 --> 00:13:23.910
How the Black Cat Pirates have fallen...

180
00:13:24.740 --> 00:13:25.990
Don't you think...

181
00:13:26.870 --> 00:13:28.450
Jango?!

182
00:13:32.750 --> 00:13:35.880
B-B-But...

183
00:13:36.960 --> 00:13:41.470
you said letting that kid go
wouldn't cause any problems!

184
00:13:44.550 --> 00:13:46.390
Yes, I did say that.

185
00:13:46.390 --> 00:13:47.470
Huh?

186
00:13:47.850 --> 00:13:50.060
And what of it?

187
00:13:50.060 --> 00:13:54.980
He was obviously going
to try and make a stand.

188
00:13:54.980 --> 00:13:57.730
The one thing I failed to account for...

189
00:13:57.730 --> 00:14:00.860
was how pathetic all of you are!

190
00:14:00.860 --> 00:14:03.740
We're... pathetic?

191
00:14:03.740 --> 00:14:05.990
Wh-Who are you calling pathetic?!

192
00:14:05.990 --> 00:14:07.660
Watch your tongue, Captain Kuro!

193
00:14:10.450 --> 00:14:12.710
Yeah, you used to be fearsome,

194
00:14:13.210 --> 00:14:15.460
but that was three years ago!

195
00:14:15.460 --> 00:14:20.380
It's not like we were taking catnaps
while you lazed around the village!

196
00:14:20.380 --> 00:14:21.840
That's right!

197
00:14:21.840 --> 00:14:26.300
We raided tons of towns and sent
loads of pirates to the bottom of the sea!

198
00:14:28.260 --> 00:14:30.060
Your point being...?

199
00:14:30.970 --> 00:14:33.980
You've done nothing for three years!

200
00:14:33.980 --> 00:14:37.360
There's no way you can beat
the Meowban Brothers anymore!

201
00:14:41.440 --> 00:14:44.410
Buchi, Sham, stop!

202
00:14:50.240 --> 00:14:52.750
You're not our captain anymore!

203
00:14:52.750 --> 00:14:55.670
Sorry, but it's time to die!

204
00:15:07.850 --> 00:15:10.600
Wh-When did he get behind them?!

205
00:15:11.180 --> 00:15:12.810
And those weapons...

206
00:15:14.730 --> 00:15:16.980
What's that about dying?

207
00:15:18.230 --> 00:15:20.190
– He snuck...
– ...behind us!

208
00:15:24.280 --> 00:15:26.320
Huh?! He's gone!

209
00:15:31.030 --> 00:15:33.370
There it is! The Pussyfoot Maneuver...

210
00:15:38.210 --> 00:15:40.290
You're right.

211
00:15:45.010 --> 00:15:48.470
I suppose I have gotten a bit slower.

212
00:15:49.300 --> 00:15:54.480
Zoro struggled with one sword, but this
guy handles them like they're kittens!

213
00:15:55.730 --> 00:16:00.060
The Pussyfoot Maneuver
allows him to move about silently.

214
00:16:00.810 --> 00:16:05.690
He could wipe out fifty assassins
before they even knew he was there!

215
00:16:06.900 --> 00:16:10.910
We have no choice
but to carry out his plan!

216
00:16:11.780 --> 00:16:17.620
I got chills when I saw
that habit of his three years later.

217
00:16:18.250 --> 00:16:24.210
The strange way he lifts his glasses to avoid
cutting his own face with those cat claws...

218
00:16:24.210 --> 00:16:27.010
is clear proof that he still
knows how to fight!

219
00:16:35.310 --> 00:16:38.480
I suppose I've gotten
a bit soft myself...

220
00:16:38.980 --> 00:16:42.560
Three years on dry land
will do that to you...

221
00:16:44.480 --> 00:16:46.570
So, I'll give you five minutes.

222
00:16:48.700 --> 00:16:52.490
If you can't clean up this mess
in the next five minutes...

223
00:16:54.490 --> 00:16:57.250
I'll kill every last one of you...

224
00:16:58.000 --> 00:17:00.670
with my own two hands!

225
00:17:09.840 --> 00:17:10.720
Five minutes...

226
00:17:11.470 --> 00:17:13.050
Five minutes should be enough!

227
00:17:14.010 --> 00:17:15.720
H-Him!

228
00:17:15.720 --> 00:17:20.810
If we just beat him,
we can get past this hill!

229
00:17:28.900 --> 00:17:31.320
We had the upper hand
against him just now!

230
00:17:31.320 --> 00:17:33.450
We'll rip him to shreds in five minutes!

231
00:17:33.950 --> 00:17:37.660
We're counting on you,
Meowban Brothers!

232
00:17:40.580 --> 00:17:41.460
Zoro!

233
00:17:45.920 --> 00:17:46.880
What?!

234
00:17:46.880 --> 00:17:48.340
H-Hey!

235
00:17:48.340 --> 00:17:50.880
You're kicking my swords now?!

236
00:17:51.840 --> 00:17:53.300
How about a "thank you"?

237
00:17:54.550 --> 00:17:55.390
Yeah...

238
00:17:56.890 --> 00:17:58.520
Thanks!

239
00:18:01.020 --> 00:18:02.270
It's no use!

240
00:18:02.270 --> 00:18:03.770
Three swords won't help...

241
00:18:03.770 --> 00:18:05.560
...if you don't know how to use 'em!

242
00:18:07.610 --> 00:18:08.360
Tiger...

243
00:18:11.860 --> 00:18:13.780
You don't get it, do you?

244
00:18:14.530 --> 00:18:16.070
...Trap!

245
00:18:20.830 --> 00:18:23.420
Four minutes.

246
00:18:26.420 --> 00:18:30.210
Just having three swords
means nothing...

247
00:18:30.210 --> 00:18:32.220
if you don't know the three-sword style!

248
00:18:37.930 --> 00:18:38.810
So...

249
00:18:42.060 --> 00:18:43.520
So strong...

250
00:18:47.810 --> 00:18:49.400
One hit...

251
00:18:58.160 --> 00:19:01.540
H-He beat the Meowban
Brothers in one hit!

252
00:19:12.710 --> 00:19:14.260
Don't worry!

253
00:19:15.180 --> 00:19:21.770
I'll take care of every last one of you
before your five minutes are up!

254
00:19:36.070 --> 00:19:38.820
Three minutes.

255
00:19:42.620 --> 00:19:46.500
I-I'll... slaughter him...

256
00:19:49.790 --> 00:19:51.920
C-Captain...

257
00:19:51.920 --> 00:19:55.090
H-Hypnotize me...

258
00:19:57.090 --> 00:19:59.550
P-Please, Captain!

259
00:20:00.100 --> 00:20:01.680
He's alive.

260
00:20:01.680 --> 00:20:03.270
You barely even scratched him.

261
00:20:05.600 --> 00:20:08.560
Guess his extra padding saved him...

262
00:20:30.080 --> 00:20:32.290
Get him, Buchi!

263
00:20:36.760 --> 00:20:39.970
Hypnosis again?!

264
00:20:43.720 --> 00:20:44.970
This guy's a pain.

265
00:20:45.470 --> 00:20:48.440
He was already strong enough
to crack the ground.

266
00:20:51.060 --> 00:20:53.570
What happens
when he's powered up?!

267
00:21:02.700 --> 00:21:04.160
Now's my chance!

268
00:21:04.160 --> 00:21:07.620
I gotta wake him up while I still can!

269
00:21:07.620 --> 00:21:10.250
What are you up to now...?

270
00:21:11.290 --> 00:21:13.000
Meddlesome girl...

271
00:21:13.420 --> 00:21:16.630
Everyone else is getting their
ass kicked while he takes a nap!

272
00:21:18.010 --> 00:21:19.340
Die!

273
00:21:23.390 --> 00:21:24.930
Get up!

274
00:21:24.930 --> 00:21:26.810
Nami! Look out!

275
00:21:31.270 --> 00:21:32.770
Split in two!

276
00:21:34.150 --> 00:21:35.400
Dodge!

277
00:21:37.070 --> 00:21:39.360
Wh-What the?!

278
00:21:40.360 --> 00:21:41.780
A chakram!

279
00:21:41.780 --> 00:21:44.240
It wasn't just for hypnosis?!

280
00:21:45.450 --> 00:21:50.290
Nami! How dare you
stomp on my face!

281
00:21:52.080 --> 00:21:53.630
H-He's alive?!

282
00:21:54.790 --> 00:21:59.050
Can't tell if he has
good or bad timing...

283
00:22:02.930 --> 00:22:04.090
L-Luffy...

284
00:22:09.520 --> 00:22:11.060
Luffy!

285
00:22:11.060 --> 00:22:13.980
Ow...

286
00:22:14.350 --> 00:22:16.730
Owww!

287
00:22:17.150 --> 00:22:19.610
H-He came back to life!

288
00:22:19.610 --> 00:22:21.440
This is bad!

289
00:22:21.440 --> 00:22:24.110
No way five minutes is enough now!

290
00:22:25.030 --> 00:22:28.200
Nami! That hurt, you jerk!

291
00:22:28.200 --> 00:22:30.160
That wasn't me!

292
00:22:30.160 --> 00:22:31.710
It wasn't...

293
00:22:35.170 --> 00:22:36.500
N-Nami?

294
00:22:36.500 --> 00:22:38.920
Did you hurt your shoulder?

295
00:22:39.960 --> 00:22:42.380
I-It's nothing. I'm fine...

296
00:22:42.380 --> 00:22:45.840
I've done everything I can for now...

297
00:22:45.840 --> 00:22:48.140
so I leave the rest to you...

298
00:22:49.180 --> 00:22:53.270
We can't lose this fight
no matter what...

299
00:22:53.270 --> 00:22:54.060
Yeah!

300
00:22:55.350 --> 00:22:58.730
Do your best for the sake
of my treasure!

301
00:22:58.730 --> 00:23:01.940
Alright! That sounds more like you!

302
00:23:03.150 --> 00:23:05.490
One minute.

303
00:23:07.820 --> 00:23:09.620
You can't be serious!

304
00:23:09.620 --> 00:23:12.040
Not even Captain Jango and Buchi...

305
00:23:12.370 --> 00:23:15.870
...can finish them in one minute!

306
00:23:26.220 --> 00:23:29.050
Buchi! There's no time to think!

307
00:23:29.800 --> 00:23:32.020
Butcher that bellyband bastard!

308
00:23:32.020 --> 00:23:36.230
I'll handle the weird brat...

309
00:23:42.780 --> 00:23:44.570
Straw Hat is mine!

310
00:23:47.160 --> 00:23:50.080
Huh? That butt-ler is here too!

311
00:23:51.030 --> 00:23:52.740
Isn't that...

312
00:23:52.740 --> 00:23:55.460
Didn't he fall off that cliff and die?

313
00:23:57.210 --> 00:23:58.500
No matter.

314
00:24:10.970 --> 00:24:12.560
Do not approach me...

315
00:24:16.020 --> 00:24:18.140
from behind!

316
00:24:18.980 --> 00:24:20.940
Kaya!

317
00:24:36.750 --> 00:24:38.670
Usopp! Are you okay?!

318
00:24:38.670 --> 00:24:40.000
K-Kaya...

319
00:24:40.000 --> 00:24:41.670
What are you doing here?!

320
00:24:42.380 --> 00:24:44.630
I'm so sorry, Usopp...

321
00:24:44.630 --> 00:24:47.470
I know you may not
accept my apology...

322
00:24:47.470 --> 00:24:49.840
but I just couldn't believe it...!

323
00:24:49.840 --> 00:24:52.760
K-Klahadore, a pirate...

324
00:24:52.760 --> 00:24:54.720
Forget about that!

325
00:24:54.720 --> 00:24:56.180
Why are you here?!

326
00:24:56.180 --> 00:24:58.230
I told you to run away!

327
00:24:58.230 --> 00:25:00.440
Your life is in danger!

328
00:25:00.440 --> 00:25:04.270
But... you're here fighting!

329
00:25:05.780 --> 00:25:09.570
Even after I treated you so horribly
and you've been hurt so badly,

330
00:25:09.570 --> 00:25:12.780
you're still fighting for me!

331
00:25:12.780 --> 00:25:13.580
That's why...

332
00:25:13.580 --> 00:25:15.160
Miss Kaya...

333
00:25:16.240 --> 00:25:18.710
Why are you here?

334
00:25:21.370 --> 00:25:24.130
S-Stop this...

335
00:25:27.300 --> 00:25:30.800
Stop this, Klahadore!

336
00:25:37.220 --> 00:25:40.190
Merry told me everything.

337
00:25:43.020 --> 00:25:45.360
Isn't that the girl from the mansion?

338
00:25:45.820 --> 00:25:48.690
So she's the target of the plan?!

339
00:25:48.690 --> 00:25:51.450
Do we even have to
go to the village now?

340
00:25:51.450 --> 00:25:53.660
We just need to kill her, right?!

341
00:25:56.790 --> 00:25:58.540
Klahadore, please!

342
00:25:58.540 --> 00:26:02.000
If you want my fortune,
you can have it all!

343
00:26:02.000 --> 00:26:03.790
Just leave this village!

344
00:26:03.790 --> 00:26:05.420
At once!

345
00:26:05.420 --> 00:26:09.630
I'm more than happy to accept, but...

346
00:26:10.130 --> 00:26:14.760
there's one other thing
I want, you see...

347
00:26:16.720 --> 00:26:19.310
What I want...

348
00:26:20.850 --> 00:26:23.190
is peace of mind.

349
00:26:23.690 --> 00:26:25.400
Peace of mind...?

350
00:26:26.150 --> 00:26:29.860
Yes. I want to be at peace.

351
00:26:31.070 --> 00:26:35.070
I've spent three years earning
the trust of the villagers here.

352
00:26:35.070 --> 00:26:40.330
The funny thing is, I've come
to take great comfort in that.

353
00:26:40.330 --> 00:26:46.880
I want to have that sort
of peace forever...

354
00:26:53.880 --> 00:26:55.590
And so...

355
00:26:56.340 --> 00:26:59.720
And so I shall be given that peace!

356
00:26:59.720 --> 00:27:02.180
As well as your fortune...

357
00:27:02.810 --> 00:27:05.150
In short, pirates will
come to the village!

358
00:27:08.270 --> 00:27:09.190
Not only that...

359
00:27:09.770 --> 00:27:12.900
but you will die
and leave behind your will!

360
00:27:13.280 --> 00:27:16.700
These two things are absolute.

361
00:27:17.280 --> 00:27:19.200
N-No...

362
00:27:20.200 --> 00:27:22.410
Y-You're not...

363
00:27:23.080 --> 00:27:26.920
Run! Run away, Kaya!
There's no use talking to him!

364
00:27:26.920 --> 00:27:28.290
Run away!

365
00:27:28.290 --> 00:27:31.250
Y-You're not Klahadore...

366
00:27:31.250 --> 00:27:33.510
You're not Klahadore!

367
00:27:34.720 --> 00:27:36.220
Kaya...

368
00:27:36.630 --> 00:27:38.050
Leave this village!

369
00:27:38.050 --> 00:27:39.470
Right this second!

370
00:27:39.800 --> 00:27:41.430
I see.

371
00:27:41.430 --> 00:27:45.390
You've certainly grown
a lot these past three years...

372
00:27:46.270 --> 00:27:48.230
Miss Kaya.

373
00:27:49.400 --> 00:27:51.730
Do you remember?

374
00:27:51.730 --> 00:27:54.820
So much has happened
in three years...

375
00:27:55.860 --> 00:28:00.070
We've spent so much time together...

376
00:28:00.070 --> 00:28:03.950
Even before your parents passed
away and you became bedridden...

377
00:28:05.040 --> 00:28:06.540
So much time...

378
00:28:10.250 --> 00:28:11.670
So many memories...

379
00:28:11.670 --> 00:28:16.300
Together we suffered,
together we rejoiced...

380
00:28:16.800 --> 00:28:19.300
K-Klahadore...

381
00:28:20.300 --> 00:28:22.310
We would visit the city together...

382
00:28:23.060 --> 00:28:25.810
and I would always look after you
when you had a fever...

383
00:28:26.810 --> 00:28:30.810
You listened to my stories
with a smile on your face...

384
00:28:32.900 --> 00:28:35.990
I devoted myself to you...

385
00:28:37.200 --> 00:28:38.990
For so long...

386
00:28:38.990 --> 00:28:41.200
Yes, for so long...

387
00:28:41.620 --> 00:28:43.870
I endured it all...

388
00:28:45.540 --> 00:28:52.380
Yes, I endured it all for this
very day when I could finally kill you!

389
00:28:59.380 --> 00:29:03.180
I, the man once known
as Captain Kuro,

390
00:29:03.510 --> 00:29:07.480
had to debase myself and put on
a smile for some snot-nosed girl!

391
00:29:08.390 --> 00:29:12.610
I cast aside my nature
and ingratiated myself to you!

392
00:29:17.440 --> 00:29:19.030
Damn you...

393
00:29:19.610 --> 00:29:22.990
Do you understand how humiliating
it was, day in and day out?

394
00:29:23.910 --> 00:29:28.710
Do you understand what that meant
for the man once known as Captain Kuro?!

395
00:29:36.090 --> 00:29:39.130
Kuro!

396
00:29:44.800 --> 00:29:47.180
Come to think of it...

397
00:29:49.520 --> 00:29:52.850
I still owe you for hitting me.

398
00:29:53.400 --> 00:29:55.060
Usopp!

399
00:29:55.400 --> 00:29:59.860
As I recall, you struck me
with everything you had...

400
00:30:23.090 --> 00:30:27.930
If you hate getting hit that much,
I got a hundred more punches for you!
